SQL_STMT_U.val: select A.CLNT101_ADMNO, A.CLNT102_CLNTNO from :1/CLNT A where A.CLNT404_ADVANCESVIAIBOL = 'Y' and A.CLNT404_ADVANCEAUTOMATIC = 'Y' and A.CLNT212_FCI = 0 and A.CLNT401_REMARKS_INTERNAL<>1 and A.CLNT212_REVERSEFACTORING ='N' and not(exists(select * from :1/CLNA where CLNA_ADMNO = A.CLNT101_ADMNO and CLNA_CLNTNO = A.CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLNA_TRANSFERRED = 'N')) and (A.CLNT404_ALLIBOLSESSIONS = 'Y' or exists(select * from :1/CLSE where CLSE_ADMNO = A.CLNT101_ADMNO and CLSE_CLNTNO = A.CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLSE_SESSION = :2)) and exists(select * from :1/CLBA where CLBA414_ADMNO = A.CLNT101_ADMNO and CLBA414_CLNTNO = A.CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLBA414_BANK_ADMNO = :3 and CLBA414_BANK_LEDG_NO = :4 and CLBA414_DEFAULTBANK = 'Y' and CLBA_WAITFORAPPROVAL = 'N') and not(exists(select * from :1/CLNT B where B.CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = A.CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO and B.CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = A.CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO and B.CLNT401_REMARKS_INTERNAL = 1 and B.CLNT906_STATUSCONTRACT <> 2)) and exists(select * from :1/SECR where SECR_ADMNO = A.CLNT101_ADMNO and SECR_CLNTNO = A.CLNT102_CLNTNO and SECR_RELEASE_SECU_SD = 'Y') for fetch only
